			<ul class="bulleted_list">
				<li>The very famous Neuro Physician Dr. Pratap Sancheti visits the hospital regularly every month.</li>
				<li>Dr. Sudheer maloo is also giving his service every week, which enhances the treatment process.</li>
				<li>Dr, Rajendra Chandak is also giving his service.</li>
				<li>All types of basic Facility is available in the hospital premises.</li>
				<li>The Hospital Incharge, Dr. Shailendra Patidar will also be available daily.</li>
				<li>The EEG (Electroencephalography) facility is also available in hospital.</li>
				<li>For the persons who cannot come every month for medicines, The Organisation is providing the medicines to their door by the help of Money Order through Indian Post. But the patient have to appear atleast once in every three months.</li>

